Project structure and examples where to look:
1. Api layer contains controllers, dtos, services => api\src\Api
2. Controllers uses services for get requests and mediatr commands for other requests. => api\src\Api\Controllers
3. Services have interfaces and implementation for those interfaces. => api\src\Api\Services
4. Application layer contains Commands, Exeptions and validators, all used in commands which are used in controllers. => api\src\Application
5. Domain layer contains models which are used in DB => api\src\Domain
6. Infrasctructure layer contains Configurations, Repositories. => api\src\Infrastructure
7. Configarations are used for mogrations to create a table in DB. => api\src\Infrastructure\Persistence\Configurations
8. Repositories used to work with DB and respective models. Repositories usually have IQueries and IRepository, check them as well. => api\src\Infrastructure\Persistence\Repositories
9. The description of project is at => PROJECT-SUMMARY.md

